<?xml version="1.0"?>
<Fleet xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <Name>Grey Wing</Name>
  <Version>3</Version>
  <TotalPoints>3000</TotalPoints>
  <FactionKey>KUIPER/kuiper</FactionKey>
  <Description>Difficulty: &lt;color=red&gt;HARD&lt;/color&gt;

Grey Wing "Warden" is an objective focused wing. The center piece of the wing is the 'Move With Purpose', a Helendir Class Line Carrier. Its role is to engage enemy cap dominance assets with its 50mm coil guns, and provide long range support to its cappers by way of its complement of 12 Zephyr multirole fighters. Said fighters are able to engage enemy light assets with their SGM-239 Derivative missiles. Or enemy craft by way of the SDM-227 Axiom and SGM-152 Consequence. Helping to manage the sensor picture is the 'Aware' a Spotting corvette. While the other five Kyves are intended to be used flexibly, either defending friendly objectives, or contesting hostile ones.
  </Description>
  <SortOverrideOrder>8</SortOverrideOrder>
  <ModDependencies>
    <unsignedLong>3649434947</unsignedLong>
  </ModDependencies>
